Titolo: Franchise Hockey Manager

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Franchise Hockey Manager, abbreviated as FHM, is a text-based ice hockey simulation for career, historical, and fictional play. "FHM creates a management simulator that offers total, believable depth in managing a hockey franchise," PopMatters said in a review.FHM's publisher, OOTP Developments, is well known as the company behind the long-running series Out of the Park Baseball.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: 71
